Mode regular:
- Sensor sampling (DONE)
- ST switch
- Temp alarm
- UART report
- Indicator regular (oled or led arr)

Mode Relay:
- Sensor sampling
- UART relay + report
- Indicator relay (oled arr)


Sensors

* LS
- sample every LS_ST
- switch ST if bright/dim in Regular Mode

* ACC
- sample zAcc
- calc variance

* TS
- sample Temp sensor (DONE)
- sound alarm in regular mode (sound alarm DONE)


Hints
- Interrupts
- SysTick
- Sensor timing

